{"tid":1130364,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［是咁的］我地TG谷想招收新成員","createTime":"2019-04-29T03:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T10:20:23.000Z","uid":81286,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b680a048377621c61cfcfa33ce2c2926c0894fc","tid":1130364,"uid":81286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我地TG谷想招收新成員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋大部份都係80-00後嘅社會棟樑<br />\n主要都係吹水派膠居多 <br />\n亦有討論生活 感情 工作 毒撚嘢 音樂 水晶 占卜 星座 時事 寵物 藝術 衫褲鞋襪 飲飲食食 量子力學 神神怪怪 亦間中有少量學術 更加唔介意大家放負求開解 無所不談 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇限住大家傾啲乜 但想下下都傾18+就借借 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要有一顆頑強嘅心 千祈唔好認真魔人同玻璃心 因為大家都鍾意抽下水mean下<br />\n因為當你自己人啊柒頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋亦會經常搞谷聚 普遍都10-20人 <br />\n歡迎大家踴躍參與(千祈唔好放飛機）<br />\n<br />\n最緊要 上水！上水！上水！<br />\n基本互相尊重 唔好講或少講令人反感既野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人<br />\n<br />\n定期清幽靈 唔係Hi就叫講嘢<br />\n唔係懶鳩有禮貌講句早晨就潛水<br />\n入完最好自我介紹下 打下招呼<br />\n講下自己鍾意啲咩 唔好又話答唔到嗲<br />\n入完谷當日唔出聲即踢<br />\n有谷友投訴 搵客 厹 睇路唔該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTG不是生活所有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019最新評價<br />\n熱鬧：★★★★★<br />\n氣氛：★★★★★<br />\n谷聚：★★★★☆ <br />\n幽靈：★☆☆☆☆<br />\n絲打：☆☆☆☆☆<br />\n<br />\nTG Link :<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/NineUpHaHaMad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNineUpHaHaMad&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9abKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=946be209\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/NineUpHaHaMad</a>"},{"pid":"adb909833be8fcd07fd3c11f379526275967edf4","tid":1130364,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"又一個月 入群pm我"},{"pid":"08347d6b61c7affae0459ae1ce3a05d6b88631d